description.en: Swampy is a governance token native to the Swamp.finance ecosystem. It's a yield optimiser hosted on Binance Smart Chain. Swampy token’s utility is for participation in voting on SwampDAO proposals where holders can vote on new vaults additions and changes to tokenomics.
